            Cazoo auction platform.
          </li>
          <li>
            Delivering incremental improvements across the funnel, focusing on key metrics such as valuation rate, offer
            rate, and acceptance rate.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </Project>

      <Project id="cazoo-operations" title="Cazoo Operations" period={{ start: "2020-09", end: "2024-02" }}>
        <p>
          I contributed significantly to the rapid scaling of operations at <a href="https://www.cazoo.co.uk/">Cazoo</a
