        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Created a solution to enable middle&#8209;mile logistics planning and execution to be brought
            in&#8209;house, ultimately scaling to support close to 160K used car sales.
          </li>
          <li>
            Reduced the launch time for Cazoo Customer Centres from 3&nbsp;weeks to 1&nbsp;hour, enabling rapid scaling
            from 1&nbsp;to&nbsp;9&nbsp;locations in less than 1&nbsp;month. This expansion increased vehicle handover
            capacity, ultimately leading to an 8%&nbsp;increase in the overall conversion rate.
          </li>
          <li>
