            <a href="https://www.uml.org"><abbr title="Unified Modeling Language">UML</abbr></a> and
            <a href="http://www.bpmn.org"><abbr title="Business Process Model and Notation">BPMN</abbr></a>.
          </li>
          <li>
            Designing RESTful APIs using <a href="https://raml.org"
              ><abbr title="RESTful API Modeling Language">RAML</abbr></a
            >.
          </li>
          <li>
            Designing a microservice orchestration capability using <a href="https://www.activiti.org">Activiti’s</a> open&#8209;source
            <abbr title="Business Process Management">BPM</abbr> framework.
          </li>
          <li>
            Integrating with HSBC core banking systems, <a href="https://www.forgerock.com">ForgeRock</a>
            <a href="https://www.forgerock.com/platform/identity-management">OpenIDM</a> and
            <a href="https://www.forgerock.com/platform/access-management">OpenAM</a>
            identity and access management services, and <a href="https://onfido.com">Onfido</a> for document identification
            and facial biometric verification services.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </Project>

