            <a href="https://www.ruby-lang.org">Ruby</a> microservices supporting a number of use cases such as application
            push notifications, <abbr title="content delivery network">CDN</abbr> purging and detecting dating scammers.
          </li>
          <li>
            Transactional email platform: A new pipeline for rendering and sending personalised member emails using
            <a href="https://www.rabbitmq.com">RabbitMQ</a> and <a href="https://www.ruby-lang.org">Ruby</a>
            microservices. Peak volumes were in excess of 20M emails per day.
